Package org.apache.log4j

Class Priority

java.lang.Object
org.apache.log4j.Level
org.apache.log4j.Priority
public class Priority extends Level
Priority class for log4j compatibility. In log4j 1.x, Priority was the parent class of Level. This maintains backward compatibility.
